<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4272867>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figs 60–65. Ischnomyia albicosta (Walker, 1849), female (Canada: Ontario, Figs 60, 64; USA: Tennessee, Figs 61–63, 65). 60 – postabdomen, dorsally; 61 – spermathecae; 62 – female internal sclerites, ventrally; 63 – ventral receptacle, sublaterally; 64 – postabdomen, ventrally; 65 – female genital chamber and S8, laterally. Scales = 0.05 mm (Figs 61, 63) and 0.1 mm (others). For abbreviation see p. 11." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4272867/files/figure.png" .

